refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
resourceeio_readdir stringpath intflags intpri callablecallback stringdataNULL
Reads through a whole directory(via the opendir, readdir and closedir system calls) and returns either the names or an array in result argument of callback function, depending on the flags argument.

&reftitle.examples;
eio_readdir example
<?php /* Is called when eio_readdir() finishes */ function my_readdir_callback($data, $result) { echo __FUNCTION__, " called\n"; echo "data: "; var_dump($data); echo "result: "; var_dump($result); echo "\n"; }
eio_readdir("/var/spool/news", EIO_READDIR_STAT_ORDER | EIO_READDIR_DIRS_FIRST, EIO_PRI_DEFAULT, "my_readdir_callback"); eio_event_loop(); ?>
&example.outputs.similar;
